        <p>Sn√¶fellsj√∂kull glacier caps an active volcano and inspired Jules Verne's "Journey to the Center of the Earth." The glacier and surrounding national park offer hiking opportunities and dramatic coastal scenery that showcases Iceland's geological diversity.</p>

